data.description: This home has an ASSUMABLE LOAN for an owner occupied new buyer. Seller has a 4% interest!!! The kitchen shines with stainless steel appliances, and the spacious dining area is perfect for gatherings. Enjoy the fresh spring breeze in the glass-enclosed and screened-in porch. Two generously sized bedrooms offer ample closet space with built-in lights. The fully fenced yard provides privacy, and there's even extra storage space in the one-car garage. Cozy up by the fireplace in the living room with a designated TV area. Plus, you'll appreciate the newer roof, HVAC system, waterproofed basement, and panel box. Don't miss this fantastic opportunity!
